Opportunity Team Member and Opportunity Contact Role
The Opportunity Team Member and Opportunity Contact Role are standard related objects whose visibility is inherently dictated by the parent Opportunity. Neither object possesses an independent Organization-Wide Default (OWD) setting; their sharing models are strictly Controlled by Parent.

Consequently, any user who successfully access to an Opportunity will implicitly inherit access to both its Team Members and Contact Roles.

